Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.36,0:00:54.73,OP,,0,0,0,,{\alpha11\pos(389.4,960.771)\fad(50,1000)\fs35.667}そ ら
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.30,0:01:13.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\alpha11\pos(708,1025.417)\fad(50,50)}黒天の蒼に溶けて　流れてく涙の粒
